  <name>Quetoo</name>
  <summary>A Free, standalone first person shooter video game</summary>
  <metadata_license>CC0-1.0</metadata_license>
  <project_license>GPL-2.0+</project_license>
  <url type="homepage">http://www.quetoo.org</url>

  <description>
    <p>
      Quetoo is a Free, standalone first person shooter video game based
      on id Tech2. Our goal is to bring the fun of oldschool deathmatch
      to a more contemporary platform, and perhaps to a new generation
      of gamers. Quetoo is multiplayer-only. There is no single-player
      or offline gameplay mode. If you have no Internet and no friends,
      Quetoo might not be for you.
    </p>
  </description>
